<div>
    Access credentials from Akeyless in Jenkins as CredentialsProvider (like AWS Secrets Manager Credentials Provider).
    Supports all Akeyless authentication methods via the Akeyless plugin.
    Configure at <a href="${rootURL}/configure">Manage Jenkins → Configure System</a> (Akeyless Credentials Provider section).
</div>
